c: 72
v: 6
t: "wanh kan rijal min al'iins ystjyrwn birijal min aljn, fzad rjal aljnn al'ins basteadhthm bihim khwfana w'irhabana wrebana. whdhh alasteadht bighayr allh, alty neaha allah ela ahl aljahlyt, min alshirk alakbr, aldhy la yghfrh allah 'iilaa baltwbt alnswh mnh. wafi alayat tahdhir shadid min alluju' 'iilaa alsaharat walmshewdhyn washbahhm"